&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Realize your potential by joining the leading performance-driven advertising company!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Data Analyst Intern – Advertising Optimization at our Budapest office- 60% position, you’ll play a key role in maximizing the performance of Dynamic Creative Optimization (DCO) campaigns for global advertisers. You’ll work hands-on with data to monitor, analyze, and optimize campaigns, ensuring they deliver strong results and actionable insights. This role blends analytical depth and technical skills with creative problem-solving, giving you exposure to real-world performance marketing at scale. It’s an opportunity to grow your technical and analytical skills in a fast-moving, data-driven environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To thrive in this role, you&#39;ll need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;B.Sc in Computer Science, Business Informatics, or related field; available ~3 days/week during internship.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong SQL and Excel skills, including advanced functions, pivot tables, and data manipulation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid grasp of statistical and mathematical concepts to interpret metrics and make data-driven decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical, logical thinker with a problem-solving mindset-&amp;nbsp; proactive in identifying and resolving issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Independent and reliable, able to manage time, own tasks end-to-end, and deliver high-quality results.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus points if you have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Python knowledge.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How you’ll make an impact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor day-to-day performance of DCO (Dynamic Creative Optimization) campaigns, ensuring they meet or exceed target KPIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage budget pacing, spending boosts and budget depletion to maximize efficiency and results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform optimization across key dimensions including sites, devices, creatives, bids and audience segments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up, monitor and evaluate advertiser-specific A/B tests — from hypothesis through execution to analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create regular reports for clients and internal stakeholders detailing performance trends, insights and recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze campaign performance and prepare insights and presentations for internal business meetings, identifying issues and recommending actionable improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
